{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/viper.png?t=1736301771\" /> <strong>CROP AND CLAW</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/viper.png?t=1736301771\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>A miasma consumes Garden.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The decay brings lawlessness</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>and madness to the land.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Rogues, cults, and evil</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>plantlife rule the realm.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crop and Claw is a classic-style JRPG centered around dragons in a lush realm known as the &quot;Garden&quot;. The plantlife has gone awry, bringing an era of struggle across the realm. One dragon sets out on adventure, for reasons only known to themselves, to see if the Garden could be restored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/snail.png?t=1736301771\" /> <strong>KEY FEATURES</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/snail.png?t=1736301771\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> * Multiple dragon types to take the role of, each with their own unique specialties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> * A continent stuffed with dungeons and secrets to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> * A simple and classic combat system focused on resource management.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> * Dragons, dragons, dragons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/lizard_swamp.png?t=1736301771\" /> <strong>REPLAYABLE</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/lizard_swamp.png?t=1736301771\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The continent of Crop and Claw is vast. With multiple playable dragon types, a timer and step counter, and few restrictions on the player's routes, Crop and Claw is feasible for challenge runs and alternate approaches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you've already gone through the game and scavenged every corner, try a Randomized run which shuffles enemies and loot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/caterpillar.png?t=1736301771\" /> <strong>CLASSIC AND REPAINTED</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/caterpillar.png?t=1736301771\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Is your computer not powerful enough for more than a few colors? Switch to Classic mode in the options for a cosmetic change back to the original visuals and music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2760970/extras/comparison.png?t=1736301771\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Copperhead","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2760970/1d07c389149a827a1899069452c5895f32aab94a.jpg"},{"name":"Croc Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2760970/10613ddbb0a8005fe90587a106ca029b89182321.jpg"},{"name":"Chameleon Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2760970/a9610cae63aafa392945536ada975ab8c11cb04d.jpg"},{"name":"Druid Master","p